<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title><%~ it.cohortName %> <%~ it.season %> Graduation Call</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#111111; font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;">

  <!-- Full-width background -->
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color:#111111; padding:24px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">

        <!-- Main card -->
        <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color:#1b1b1b; border-radius:16px; overflow:hidden;">
          <!-- Header strip -->
          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="background-color:#000000; padding:24px 24px 20px 24px;">
              <h1 style="margin:0; font-size:22px; color:#ffffff; font-weight:700;">
                &#127891; Graduation Call Today!
              </h1>
              <p style="margin:8px 0 0 0; font-size:14px; color:#f9b233; font-weight:500;">
                <%~ it.cohortName %> <%~ it.season %>
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Body copy -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:24px 32px 16px 32px; color:#eaeaea; font-size:14px; line-height:1.6;">
              <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;">
                Hello <strong style="color:#ffd580;"><%~ it.userName %></strong>,
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0;">
                Congratulations on successfully completing the Bitshala
                <strong style="color:#f9b233;"><%~ it.cohortName %> <%~ it.season %></strong> cohort! &#127881;
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0;">
                To celebrate, we invite you to the Graduation Call where we'll reflect on the journey,
                recognize participants, and discuss what's next in the Bitshala ecosystem.
              </p>

              <!-- Session details block -->
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color:#262626; border-radius:12px; margin:0 0 20px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:16px 20px;">
                    <h3 style="margin:0 0 12px 0; font-size:16px; color:#ffd580;">
                      &#128197; Graduation Call
                    </h3>
                    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="color:#eaeaea; font-size:14px; line-height:2;">
                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding-right:10px;">&#128197;</td>
                        <td style="font-weight:600;"><%~ it.sessionDate %></td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding-right:10px;">&#9200;</td>
                        <td style="font-weight:600;"><%~ it.sessionTime %></td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding-right:10px;">&#128205;</td>
                        <td style="font-weight:600;"><%~ it.channelName %></td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0; font-weight:600; color:#ffd580;">
                During the call we will:
              </p>

              <!-- Agenda list -->
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color:#262626; border-radius:12px; margin:0 0 20px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:16px 20px;">
                    <ul style="padding-left:18px; margin:0; color:#eaeaea; font-size:13px; line-height:1.9;">
                      <li>&#127942; Celebrate your achievements</li>
                      <li>&#128220; Share your Proof of Work certificates</li>
                      <li>&#128640; Discuss Bitshala Fellowships and opportunities to contribute to Bitcoin FOSS</li>
                      <li>&#129309; Explore how to stay involved in the Bitshala community</li>
                    </ul>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;">
                This cohort is just the beginning of your journey into the Bitcoin FOSS ecosystem.
                We're excited to see what you build next.
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 4px 0; font-weight:500;">
                Looking forward to celebrating with you!
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer / sign-off -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:0 32px 28px 32px; color:#b3b3b3; font-size:14px; line-height:1.6;">
              <p style="margin:0;">
                Best regards,<br />
                <strong style="color:#eaeaea;">Team Bitshala</strong>
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
        <!-- /Main card -->

      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

</body>
</html>
